home/up_arrow.png?t=2016121614"></ul></li><li class="content-item" comment-id="o8tmiv2ive4j"><img class="avatar" src="http://s.go2yd.com/a/thead_baozheng.png"><div class="comment-hd"><span class="name">若轻如许</span><div class="right-info"><span class="date">2016.6.16</span></div></div><p>有胃病喝水还是有一些讲究的</p><div class="like-reply-part"><span class="like-num">13</span><img class="icon like-icon-btn" src="http://staticimg.yidianzixun.com/media/feeb5aea7bce8838810507e346bdef7d.png"><span class="reply-num">3</span><a class="icon reply-icon-btn">收起</a></div><ul class="comments-reply-list" style="display: block; "><li class="reply-item" reply-id="o8vfps2623ad"><img class="avatar-reply" src="http://i3.go2yd.com/avatar/group2/M04/77/CD/CmcRJ1dSrdiAay8sAACMRvifNqQ7592325.jpg?compress=7&amp;size=120x120"><div class="reply-content"><span class="name">797640550:</span><span class="content">啥讲究？</span></div><div class="right-info"><a class="icon-reply">回复</a><span class="date">2016.6.16</span></div></li><li class="reply-item" reply-id="o8wewk2ive4j"><img class="avatar-reply" src="http://s.go2yd.com/a/thead_baozheng.png"><div class="reply-content"><span class="name">若轻如许<span class="reply-words">回复</span>797640550:</span><span class="content">饭前饭后半小时，不喝水和汤，平时不能一口猛喝一大杯，激烈运动后不能马上大量饮水。不能喝凉水，温度也不能过高。早上也不能大量喝水，睡前也不能大量喝水。如果是在养病，有些药，不能大量喝水，有些要喝水。如果是在胃病急性期，还得特别注意饮食。这些都是一些常识吧</span></div><div class="right-info"><a class="icon-reply">回复</a><span class="date">2016.6.17</span></div></li><li class="reply-item" reply-id="o8wrhj2623ad"><img class="avatar-reply" src="http://i3.go2yd.com/avatar/group2/M04/77/CD/CmcRJ1dSrdiAay8sAACMRvifNqQ7592325.jpg?compress=7&amp;size=120x120"><div class="reply-content"><span class="name">797640550:</span><span class="content">谢谢！就是适合减肥人的方法我都不能用！得往胖里走！我说呢，这几天喝过水后，胃就往死里疼！以后会注意的！</span></div><div class="right-info"><a class="icon-reply">回复</a><span class="date">2016.6.17</span></div></li><img class="icon-reply-img" src="http://staticimg.yidianzixun.com/media/8dff86e125